{"tid":782833,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"創33年內最大比數反勝 辛尼特好牙擦","createTime":"2018-08-17T05:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T09:05:28.000Z","uid":153600,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"09bc68c33c70c6ffb21bb785d8252de8f6ae40f6","tid":782833,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:32:53.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=0ME6ik%2BdFVAdTzaqX0vXmQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=014aacaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】球迷奇遇記！俄超辛尼特於歐霸盃第3圈外圍賽，首回合落後0:4下，周四特次回合加時8:1大炒白俄羅斯球隊明斯克戴拿模，總比數8:5晉級。賽後，官方在社交網絡牙擦一番。<br />\n<br />\n次回合大落後下逆轉的比賽不少，但如辛尼特般大比數卻少之有少。主隊的辛尼特憑里安度柏利迪斯和諾保亞入球先追兩球，可惜柏利迪斯於72分鐘兩黃一紅出場令球隊要10人應戰。<br />\n<br />\n惟俄羅斯國腳迪斯尤巴卡6分鐘梅開二度，將比數追至4:4要踢加時。加時明斯克戴拿模雖然先入1球，但踢少個的辛尼特有迪奧斯、迪斯尤巴的入球，加上中場羅拔馬克連入兩球，最終以8:1完場，兩回合辛尼特以8:5反勝晉級，亦是歐霸盃33年來最大比數的反勝。<br />\n<br />\n賽後辛尼特的官方Twitter更自信地說：「不知道你們在擔心甚麼。」值是一提的是，今場比賽主場出擊的辛尼特因球迷被禁止入場只得少量觀眾，大批辛尼特支持者於場外的遊艇上唱歌搖旗慶祝。辛尼特晉級歐霸附加賽後，將會與由前曼聯射手蘇斯克查領軍的莫迪爭入分組賽。<br />\n<br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c511614cd1adc5ba33754d11c3549aa582ec1dcd","tid":782833,"uid":76753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:39:25.000Z","msg":"打多個都可以加時俾人入4粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c224eda73e65e411d099a2eb5bc9985841bbbd8","tid":782833,"uid":55800,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:40:11.000Z","msg":"好撚鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n辛尼特有咩可能首回合會輸四粒俾明斯克<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 唔賭波"},{"pid":"63cb12afdfd55d5532fb61c4dd5ee98930d35eb5","tid":782833,"uid":163207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:41:24.000Z","msg":"We did it<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c3a00da4ee91230df2a8458355c3b26dbd6c35","tid":782833,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:42:51.000Z","msg":"歐霸盃有撚33年"},{"pid":"63b2668d6fa70f541b819adcd00128e066247a25","tid":782833,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5c3a00da4ee91230df2a8458355c3b26dbd6c35","tid":782833,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:42:51.000Z","msg":"歐霸盃有撚33年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:53:01.000Z","msg":"佢應該係計埋舊的歐洲足協杯"},{"pid":"33ec215876d2aba09c4862d82965cede5a0fa4b4","tid":782833,"uid":140548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:53:32.000Z","msg":"開打前買辛尼特晉級賠幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcffa97d391a4bb4ee6ba2f04c6bc3c5665883d6","tid":782833,"uid":153600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5c224eda73e65e411d099a2eb5bc9985841bbbd8","tid":782833,"uid":55800,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:40:11.000Z","msg":"好撚鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n辛尼特有咩可能首回合會輸四粒俾明斯克<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 唔賭波"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:54:22.000Z","msg":"東歐主場通常都好伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c156555e6652d4ed1bc04c7c4aaf67e8d8dd4ede","tid":782833,"uid":133787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T05:55:34.000Z","msg":"咁撚假波"},{"pid":"1458145828ebfc34c5ed599c496391e37dda529c","tid":782833,"uid":43557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedB